<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这一天终于来了！<delay20 />你问是什么日子？
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />会搬来一位新居民！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能增加伙伴<delay8 />真的很让人开心。<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们得施以援手，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让新伙伴尽快熟悉这座<tag a="110" b="32" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />已经<delay20 />
和新搬来的人<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />见过面了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我也想尽快去打声招呼，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但如果对方还没整理好行李，<delay8 />
可能会感到困扰呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay8 />今天有新居民<delay8 />
搬过来了对吧？<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />得赶快去打声招呼！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已经和今天搬来的人见过面了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我<delay8 />还没去呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这种时候，<delay8 />第一印象是很重要的对吧？<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要先稍微给自己鼓鼓劲，<delay8 />
然后再去打招呼！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="011_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天<delay8 />是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的<delay8 />
生日！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />来说，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是一年一度的特殊日子<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家来一起庆祝吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay8 />
明天是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的生日！<delay20 />
你已经<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />准备好生日礼物了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经准备好了！<delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我是这么想的，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但对方会不会喜欢我的礼物，<delay8 />
在送出手之前无人可知呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的生日吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />于我而言，<delay8 />我已经不会像从前一样<delay8 />
仅仅因为是生日就兴高采烈了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也正是如此，<delay8 />现在的我才能发自内心地<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因大家来为我庆生而感到喜悦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="013_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天早上就要和<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />道别了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要笑着送行<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />在别人踏上新的旅途时
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />含泪送行，<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />那就太不知趣了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天早上，<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />就要离开这座<tag a="110" b="32" />了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
如果你还有想要传达的事情，<delay8 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在就是最后的机会！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay8 />
打包好了行李<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像明早就要<delay8 />离开这座<tag a="110" b="32" />了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人生在世，离别自然在所难免，<delay8 />
但无论经历多少次，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这份寂寥还是一如既往呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
